# PyInstaller intermediate artifacts. windows-scanner/build.sh regenerates
# these on each build; we never commit them. The deployed binary at
# windows-scanner/dist/BilalDriveMan-Scanner.exe IS committed (auto-update
# fetches it from GitHub raw), but the build/ tree and the .spec file are
# transient.
windows-scanner/build/
windows-scanner/__pycache__/
windows-scanner/*.spec
